{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fe64556ed6","title":"和干树声的谈话叫","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3ee568fd21","index":0,"year":1944,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"fe64556ed6"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"ad9638bf52","name":"王树声","type":"人物"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji19","name":"毛泽东全集第19卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji19.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji19":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"82951a64c6","type":"paragraph","text":"和干树声的谈话叫","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"fe64556ed6"},{"id":"94a16a8141","type":"paragraph","text":"（1944年）你分析得很精辟。中央也考虑，想派徐向前、戴季英、刘子久等同志和你一道，带一支生力军，速往中原，跟先期活动在那里的皮定均、徐子荣部会合，组成河南军区，发动群众，把汤恩伯丢下的大批武器捡起来，搞好根据地，抗战到底，夺取最后胜利[1]时值抗日战争已进入决战决胜的阶段，王树声一心想要上前线。这是毛泽东听他分析了中原战局后和他谈话的一部分。1944年9月，王树声季","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"fe64556ed6"}],"page":{"id":"fb8724b5ee","publicationId":"maoquanji19","articleId":"fe64556ed6","start":261,"end":261}}}},"__N_SSG":true}